show.title: The Secret Doctor Mommy
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/4UCagk
show.description: Dr. Meera, a brilliant physician living a double life as a devoted mother and secret doctor. As her carefully hidden identity begins to surface, tensions rise with Ranvijay, a powerful figure from her past, and Dadi, whose instincts sense the truth. With love for her child and loyalty to her profession clashing, Meera must protect her secret while navigating emotional stakes, complex relationships, and a world that’s closing in.
